{"ID":107,"post_author":"0","post_date":"2025-10-19 22:01:07","post_date_gmt":"2025-10-19 22:01:07","post_content":"$(cat \/home\/dave\/skippy\/work\/wordpress\/rundaverun-local\/20251106_134609_zip_code_corrections\/page_107_fixed.html)","post_title":"Our Plan","post_excerpt":"","post_status":"publish","comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","post_password":"","post_name":"our-plan","to_ping":"","pinged":"","post_modified":"2025-11-06 18:47:36","post_modified_gmt":"2025-11-06 18:47:36","post_content_filtered":"<div style=\"padding: 60px 20px;max-width: 1200px;margin: 0 auto\">\n<h1 style=\"color: #003f87;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 40px\">Our Plan for Louisville<\/h1>\n<p style=\"font-size: 1.3em;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 50px\">Same $1.2 billion budget. No new taxes. Just better priorities.<\/p>\n\n<div style=\"grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));gap: 40px;margin-bottom: 60px\">\n\n<div style=\"background: #E6F2FF;padding: 40px;border-radius: 10px\">\n<h2 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-bottom: 20px\">46 Mini Police Substations<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 1.1em;line-height: 1.8;margin-bottom: 20px\"><strong>Investment:<\/strong> $77.4M<\/p>\n<ul style=\"line-height: 2\">\n<li>Officers permanently assigned to YOUR neighborhood<\/li>\n<li>5-minute response times instead of 15-45 minutes<\/li>\n<li>Community trust building through daily interaction<\/li>\n<li>Proven to reduce crime 20-40% in other cities<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<a href=\"\/policy\/?search=substation\" style=\"color: #003f87;font-weight: 600\">Read Full Plan \u2192<\/a>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"background: #E6F2FF;padding: 40px;border-radius: 10px\">\n<h2 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-bottom: 20px\">24% Compounded Raises<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 1.1em;line-height: 1.8;margin-bottom: 20px\"><strong>Investment:<\/strong> $27.4M Year 1, $136.6M over 4 years<\/p>\n<ul style=\"line-height: 2\">\n<li>Competitive pay to retain experienced employees<\/li>\n<li>Match surrounding counties who pay more<\/li>\n<li>Better employees = better services for you<\/li>\n<li>Reduce turnover and training costs<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<a href=\"\/policy\/?search=employee+compensation\" style=\"color: #003f87;font-weight: 600\">Read Full Plan \u2192<\/a>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"background: #E6F2FF;padding: 40px;border-radius: 10px\">\n<h2 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-bottom: 20px\">18 Community Wellness Centers<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 1.1em;line-height: 1.8;margin-bottom: 20px\"><strong>Investment:<\/strong> $34.2M<\/p>\n<ul style=\"line-height: 2\">\n<li>Healthcare access in every neighborhood<\/li>\n<li>Mental health and addiction services<\/li>\n<li>Preventive care instead of just emergency rooms<\/li>\n<li>Saves $3 for every $1 spent<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<a href=\"\/policy\/?search=wellness\" style=\"color: #003f87;font-weight: 600\">Read Full Plan \u2192<\/a>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"background: #E6F2FF;padding: 40px;border-radius: 10px\">\n<h2 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-bottom: 20px\">$15M Participatory Budgeting<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 1.1em;line-height: 1.8;margin-bottom: 20px\"><strong>Your Voice:<\/strong> You decide how it is spent<\/p>\n<ul style=\"line-height: 2\">\n<li>Residents directly vote on budget priorities<\/li>\n<li>Proven successful in 50+ U.S. cities<\/li>\n<li>Real democracy, not just lip service<\/li>\n<li>YOUR neighborhood, YOUR priorities<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<a href=\"\/policy\/?search=participatory\" style=\"color: #003f87;font-weight: 600\">Read Full Plan \u2192<\/a>\n<\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"background: #FFD700;padding: 50px;border-radius: 10px;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 60px\">\n<h2 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-bottom: 30px\">See How This Changes Your Daily Life<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 1.2em;margin-bottom: 30px\">Numbers don't tell the whole story. Read real scenarios showing how this budget changes a typical day in Louisville for real people.<\/p>\n<a href=\"\/policy\/a-day-in-the-life-how-the-budget-changes-your-louisville\/\" class=\"button\" style=\"background: #003f87;color: white;padding: 15px 40px;border-radius: 50px;text-decoration: none;font-weight: 600;font-size: 1.1em\">Read: A Day in the Life<\/a>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"background: #003f87;color: white;padding: 50px;border-radius: 10px;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 60px\">\n<h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 30px\">Browse All 51 Policy Documents<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 1.2em;margin-bottom: 30px\">Every detail. Every number. Every plan. All available for you to review.<\/p>\n<a href=\"\/policy\/\" class=\"button\" style=\"background: #FFD700;color: #003f87;padding: 15px 40px;border-radius: 50px;text-decoration: none;font-weight: 600;font-size: 1.1em\">View Policy Library<\/a>\n<\/div>\n\n<\/div>","post_parent":0,"guid":"http:\/\/rundaverun-local.local\/our-plan\/","menu_order":0,"post_type":"page","post_mime_type":"","comment_count":"0","url":"http:\/\/rundaverun-local.local\/our-plan\/"}
